'''2MASS J03552337+1133437''' ('''2MASS J0355+11''') is a nearby [[brown dwarf]] of [[spectral type]] L5γ,{{r|Cruz2009}} located in constellation [[Taurus (constellation)|Taurus]] at approximately 29.8 [[light-year]]s from Earth.{{r|Liu2013}}

==Discovery==
2MASS J0355+11 was discovered in 2006 by Reid ''et al.''{{r|Reid2006}}

